responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D22F4869449795FF7C4ECB83E70F9CC8", "As commander of the Settler Militia, I must caution you from travelling within the outskirts of Lionhold. The bandits have organized to form a new more powerful threat. If you must travel, stay cloe to the roads and within convoys.")
